---
title: Bengal Roasted Cauliflower Curry with Basmati Rice
description: This delightful curry will knock your socks off with its ease and taste. The Indian-inspired Bengal curry paste is a mild yet flavourful base of ginger, chilli, turmeric and fenugreek seeds, and it works perfectly with the roasted cauliflower, carrot and greens to make a mouth-watering meal that's packed with veggie goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-cauliflower-bengal-curry-01395b72.jpg
